trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>, specifying the concrete MIME type for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett utökningsbarhet element som lagts till i en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref>, ange konkreta MIME skriver för den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref> som den <xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""> </xref> gäller.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.target: Specifikationen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/ Läs mer om Web Services WSDL (Description Language).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of MIME extensibility elements for the part of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> of which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> is a member.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar de element för MIME-utökningsbarhet för en del av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref> som den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref> är medlem.

trans-unit.source: This collection must have at least one member.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen måste ha minst en medlem.

trans-unit.source: If it has more than one member, the members are alternative MIME formats for the current <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>.
trans-unit.target: Om den har mer än en medlem är medlemmar alternativa MIME-format för aktuellt <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>

trans-unit.source: Members can be of the following types: - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding> Each of these classes exposes a `Part` property specifying the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> with which the `MimePart` is associated.
trans-unit.target: Medlemmar kan vara av följande typer:- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding>var och en av dessa klasser visar en `Part` egenskapen anger den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>som den `MimePart` associeras.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding>

trans-unit.source: If this collection has no members, the XML Web service will fail to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file when it is requested.
trans-unit.target: Om det finns inga medlemmar i den här samlingen, misslyckas XML-webbtjänsten att generera en Web Services WSDL (Description Language)-fil när den begärs.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how MIME extends WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Mer information om hur MIME utökar WSDL finns i specifikationen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
